metadata.title: Morigins Home Garden Heart Trio 12.5 x 18 Inch Decorative Valentine Love Design Garden Flag
features: Text correctly readable on double sided.
Beautiful design---colorful, vibrant, bright designs from creative, original artwork.
Flags hang beautifully from a sewn-in sleeve and it’s easy to switch out our seasonal flag.
description: At Home Garden, we are proud to be creating the best decorative garden products on the market. We have a variety of flags for all moments in your life. Be it spring, summer, autumn or winter, a national holiday or a statement of belief, we have flags for every occasion. Our original artwork printed on polyester material designed for outdoor display provides unique designs that are as durable as they are beautiful! There are many uses for our flags; as a pretty present to give to a loved one, a funny joke hanging from your porch to make your neighbors laugh, or a unique tapestry to hang in your home. We are always adding fun, new designs so be sure to check back frequently!
